    "image_with_text_Xn7zN4": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_YmYyqT": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Future sustainability",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_EGr8BP": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With many smaller initiatives underway and planned, the next five years of The Gaia Project will see Mission undertaking a major project delivering large scale tree planting of the gullies and hills surrounding its Taradale home and vineyards. This will allow us to naturally and responsibly offset our own carbon footprint.</p><p>As guardians of our place for more than 170 years, Mission will continue to work hard toward delivering positive sustainability initiatives and making some of New Zealand’s finest wines in the most energy efficient and environmentally friendly manner.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
